  </div>
  <div class="past-clients_link">
    <p>If you want to learn about my complete <strong>UX Design process</strong>, please <a href="https://medium.com/@agusfeijoo/comprehensive-description-of-my-design-process-6c004f2970f8" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">read this article</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

